Description:
    Create a new resource map plugin at plugins/. Pass the plugin name as an argument,
    either CamelCased or snake_cased.

Example:
    rails generate plugin Alerts

    Create 
        plugins/alerts/assets/
        plugins/alerts/controllers/
        plugins/alerts/controllers/alerts_controller.rb
        plugins/alerts/models/
        plugins/alerts/views/
        plugins/alerts/views/alerts/
        plugins/alerts/views/alerts/index.html
        plugins/alerts/spec/
        plugins/alerts/spec/spec_helper.rb
        plugins/alerts/plugin.rb

